name: Pixel Graffiti #01 // Throw Up Blue
description: Pixel editions of my throwies. I've painted these on walls and trains all over the world. You need to be fast when you tag or bomb with graffiti, and you need to be fast with NFTs. That's why we're bombing these throwups in the metaverse. Every edition in this series is a unique, hand drawn design. Thanks for your support, Dr.Ank
